{"title":"Sim Works Fun 3 Bar CrMo is Back in Stock","link":"https://theradavist.com/sim-works-fun-3-bar-crmo/","date":1734702495000,"content":"<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-31-1600x1067-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-31-1600x1067-2.jpg?w=650&amp;quality=75 640w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-31-1600x1067-2.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-31-1600x1067-2.jpg?w=2000&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p><em>After being sold out for an extended hiatus, the beloved <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/nitto/\" target=\"_blank\">Nitto</a>-made <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/tag/sim-works/\" target=\"_blank\">Sim Works</a> Fun 3 Bar is back with a major update…</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-45-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-45-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-45-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-45-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-66-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-66-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=400&amp;quality=75 800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-66-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;quality=75 1600w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/12/Crmo_fun3-66-1-1600x1067-1.jpg?w=1400&amp;quality=75\" /></p>\n<p>A Sim Works icon for over a decade, the updated <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/fun-3-bar\" target=\"_blank\">Fun 3 bar</a> ($90) is now offered in lightweight Chromoly tubing, offering a comfortable, capable bar with ergonomic considerations in spades. That unique triple bend shape is instantly recognizable while providing an additional segment for a handrest or a place to mount some accessories.</p>\n<p>Each Fun 3 Bar has a custom decal kit, so you can style it to your liking.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Material: CrMo Steel</li>\n<li>Width: 680mm</li>\n<li>Weight: 525g</li>\n<li>Clamp diameter: 25.4mm</li>\n<li>Grip Diameter: 22.2mm</li>\n<li>Rise: 25mm</li>\n<li>Sweep: 35°(Back) / 1.5°(Up)</li>\n<li>Finish: Silver Dullbright / Black</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.sim.works/products/fun-3-bar\" target=\"_blank\">SimWorks</a>!</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/sim-works-fun-3-bar-crmo/\">Sim Works Fun 3 Bar CrMo is Back in Stock</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"8749dfcf28910fe125d5571f55103b2116010f9ef93cfe4ca10d58fefe9ce4e8","category":"Cycling"}